caption:
Our country’s brave veterans deserve a life of peace after serving our country and protecting our freedoms. Far too many veterans are suffering. As a country, we should demand our local officials always prioritize veteran healthcare access and affordability, including mental health care. No homeless veteran should be left on the street, or feel they can’t afford to keep themselves or their families afloat. 

We must always help our veterans first. Let’s do our part to make sure no veteran is left behind after putting their lives on the line for all of us.
